{"image_id": "NSC_2017_page_56", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Deferred Tax Assets and Liabilities", "bbox": [104.2, 87.7, 445.0, 110.6]}, {"text": "Certain items are reported in different periods for financial reporting and income tax purposes.  Deferred tax assets", "bbox": [104.2, 142.6, 1156.4, 165.5]}, {"text": "and liabilities are recorded in recognition of these differences.  The tax effects of temporary differences that give", "bbox": [104.2, 170.1, 1136.4, 193.0]}, {"text": "rise to significant portions of the deferred tax assets and deferred tax liabilities are as follows:", "bbox": [104.2, 197.6, 962.7, 220.5]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [984.4, 240.7, 1117.7, 263.7]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [968.8, 274.1, 1014.6, 297.0]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [1087.5, 274.1, 1133.3, 297.0]}, {"text": "($ in millions)", "bbox": [986.1, 305.2, 1116.0, 328.1]}, {"text": "Deferred tax assets:", "bbox": [109.4, 336.4, 290.1, 359.3]}, {"text": "Compensation and benefits, including postretirement benefits", "bbox": [134.4, 367.7, 698.3, 390.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [942.7, 367.7, 954.2, 390.6]}, {"text": "235", "bbox": [1004.8, 367.7, 1039.2, 390.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1061.5, 367.7, 1072.9, 390.6]}, {"text": "464", "bbox": [1123.5, 367.7, 1157.9, 390.6]}, {"text": "Accruals, including casualty and other claims", "bbox": [134.4, 398.9, 551.9, 421.8]}, {"text": "64", "bbox": [1016.2, 398.9, 1039.2, 421.8]}, {"text": "102", "bbox": [1123.5, 398.9, 1157.9, 421.8]}, {"text": "Other", "bbox": [134.4, 430.2, 186.6, 453.1]}, {"text": "67", "bbox": [1016.2, 430.2, 1039.2, 453.1]}, {"text": "62", "bbox": [1135.0, 430.2, 1157.9, 453.1]}, {"text": "Total gross deferred tax assets", "bbox": [146.9, 461.4, 422.7, 484.3]}, {"text": "366", "bbox": [1004.8, 461.4, 1039.2, 484.3]}, {"text": "628", "bbox": [1123.5, 461.4, 1157.9, 484.3]}, {"text": "Less valuation allowance", "bbox": [134.4, 492.7, 366.0, 515.6]}, {"text": "(44)", "bbox": [1008.6, 492.7, 1046.8